c=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGxkaMAM.jpg&h=49928b96&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"39a4f06db9ec824761b138f611fb049e297247bf","tid":2031663,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T14:22:41.000Z","msg":"正吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />記得Be water my friends<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n謹記適時保持兩米距離排排企<br />\n我鍾意排隊等巴士<br />\n排隊食黃店<br />\n企定定睇熱鬧<br />\n地少人多，閒閒地都<br />\n1000人、10000人、100000人、1000000人<br />\n隊形痴埋一齊都好正常<br />\n<br />\n文宣係咩？紙囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n加卡版、咪變硬卡紙囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n天口熱、撥下涼姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n狗狗鍾意票控咪由得佢囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n抄佢老母票、抄到佢天荒地老<br />\n彌敦道出九龍大老山隧道獅子山入口再出港島太平山<br />\n同我罰抄<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n抄到無紙<br />\n呃佢老母ot錢<br />\n法庭忙到甩轆<br />\n最後原來得個吉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n乜都唔洗罰<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n鍾意講咩玩咩都係自由意志<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個post令我明白p牌嘅價值<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n妙獲負皮，明明得我自彈自唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多一個人理就即刻放負一隻<br />\n<br />\n證明咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n吖媽我得左啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n五毛加持嘅大絕<br />\n使出香港人大技-人海戰術<br />\n排排企食果果<br />\n破佢老母限聚令<br />\n<br />\n兄弟努力 各自爬山<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2031264\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2031264</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n反其道而行，先係破局<br />\n同狗玩數字遊戲無意思<br />\n要玩就黎舖曬冷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e01adbc5f55e652041de0a71b8797ce42a2d2d2f","tid":2031663,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T14:26:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3b18f8290730e14ae38bed0ed0f691206528ff1","tid":2031663,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T14:27:15.000Z","msg":"有好野就要益街坊"},{"pid":"15655c9ce417469f388dcab8deb9591982dc8044","tid":2031663,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T14:28:39.000Z","msg":"手握文宣，立地成佛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b212c45c0dfaccfe2c3b0109e4d22bd1320df59","tid":2031663,"uid":291603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T15:15:31.000Z","msg":"great design adore"},{"pid":"4a79f8fdd121ca6184a1175c22af967cc67fa662","tid":2031663,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"faee939d14598b755da47b0e20d9edd069e6f593","tid":2031663,"uid":323420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T14:15:00.000Z","msg":"掉左先好走<br />\n<br />\n引玉！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qoYjEUk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqoYjEUk.jpg&h=d5233391&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https